{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1>nfs</h1>\n<p>总而言之 一种类似文件共享的机制 能够使得你访问其他机器上的文件\n<a href=\"https://linuxize.com/post/how-to-mount-an-nfs-share-in-linux/\">how-to-mount-nfs</a></p>\n<h1>verify</h1>\n<p>showmount -e IP</p>\n<h1>mount</h1>\n<p>sudo mount -t nfs 10.10.0.10:/backups /var/backups </p>\n<h1>fstab</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-sh line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-sh\"># &lt;file system&gt;     &lt;dir&gt;       &lt;type&gt;   &lt;options&gt;   &lt;dump&gt;\t&lt;pass&gt;\n10.10.0.10:/backups /var/backups  nfs      defaults    0       0</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>","fields":{"slug":"/cube/nfs/","disqus":{"shortname":"woodgear-blog"}},"frontmatter":{"id":"ktxpwmp","time":"1996-09-08T23:37:07+08:00","tag":null},"parent":{"__typename":"File","name":"nfs","ext":".md","birthTime":"1970-01-01T00:00:00.000Z","changeTime":"2020-09-26T05:06:56.578Z","relativeDirectory":"cube","absolutePath":"/home/oaa/ns/share/blog/cube/nfs.md"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/cube/nfs/","disqus":{"shortname":"woodgear-blog"}}}